    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图来描述数据加载流程。系统从Redis缓存开始，先进入空闲状态，收到请求后开始加载。加载成功就返回成功状态，失败的话要能重试，但如果连续失败就得交给WorkerNode去处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是Infra_RedisCache。那从Success和Error回到Idle的触发条件分别是什么？还有Error到WorkerNode的'Abort'是终止整个流程的意思吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Success",
        "Idle",
        "Error",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Success到Idle是'Reset'，就是重置后等待新请求。Error到Idle是'Retry'，重试机制。Error到WorkerNode的'Abort'是放弃当前请求，转给后台节点异步处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Success",
        "Idle",
        "Error",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画第一版：RedisCache指向Idle，Idle通过'Start Request'到Loading，Loading分叉到Success和Error。两个终态都能回Idle，Error额外连到WorkerNode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Loading到Success的触发条件我写错了，应该是'Data Received'，不是'Response OK'。还有Loading到Error应该是'Request Failed'，不是'Timeout'，超时只是失败的一种情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，修正为Loading--Success是'Data Received'，Loading--Error是'Request Failed'。其他连线标签：Idle到Loading是'Start Request'，Success回Idle是'Reset'，Error回Idle是'Retry'，Error到WorkerNode是'Abort'，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
